#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn37.14"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn37.14:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 37 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 37 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.14:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamapeyyālavagga "
msgstr "1. Abbreviated Texts "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn37.14:0.3"
msgid "14. Pañcaverasutta "
msgstr "14. Five Threats "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn37.14:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, anuruddha, dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo … pe … nirayaṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "“Anuruddha, when females have five qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell. "

msgctxt "sn37.14:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "sn37.14:1.3"
msgid "Pāṇātipātī ca hoti, adinnādāyī ca hoti, kāmesumicchācārī ca hoti, musāvādī ca hoti, surāmerayamajjappamādaṭṭhāyī ca hoti—"
msgstr "They kill living creatures, steal, commit sexual misconduct, lie, and consume alcoholic drinks that cause negligence. "

msgctxt "sn37.14:1.4"
msgid "imehi kho, anuruddha, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato mātugāmo kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjatī”ti. "
msgstr "When females have these five qualities, when their body breaks up, after death, they are reborn in a place of loss, a bad place, the underworld, hell.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.14:1.5"
msgid "Cuddasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn37.14:1.6"
msgid "Paṭhamapeyyālavaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
#. VAR: puriso ca → dve manāpā amanāpā ca (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.1"
msgid "Mātugāmo puriso ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: tidhammo ca → āveṇiko tīhi dhammehi (bj) | āveṇikā tīhi anuruddho (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.2"
msgid "āveṇikā tidhammo ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.3"
msgid "Kodhano upanāhī ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.4"
msgid "issukī maccharena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.5"
msgid "Aticārī ca dussīlo, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.6"
msgid "appassuto ca kusīto; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.7"
msgid "Muṭṭhassati pañcaveraṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn37.14:2.8"
msgid "kaṇhapakkhe pakāsito. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
